{
  "book": "1nephi",
  "bookName": "1 Nephi",
  "chapter": 10,
  "voice": {
    "provider": "elevenlabs",
    "voice_id": "ddDFRErfhdc2asyySOG5",
    "model_id": "eleven_multilingual_v2",
    "settings": {
      "stability": 0.5,
      "similarity_boost": 0.75,
      "style": 0.35,
      "use_speaker_boost": true
    },
    "name": "Samuel"
  },
  "pauses": {
    "line_ms": 180,
    "verse_ms": 500
  },
  "duration": 340.371,
  "lines": [
    {
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 3.529,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And now I, Nephi, proceed to give a account upon these plates",
      "verse": "10:1",
      "lineIndex": 1
    },
    {
      "start": 3.709,
      "end": 6.449,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "of my proceedings, and my reign and ministry;",
      "verse": "10:1",
      "lineIndex": 2
    },
    {
      "start": 6.629,
      "end": 9.137,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "wherefore, to proceed with mine account,",
      "verse": "10:1",
      "lineIndex": 3
    },
    {
      "start": 9.317,
      "end": 12.196,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I must speak somewhat of the things of my father,",
      "verse": "10:1",
      "lineIndex": 4
    },
    {
      "start": 12.376,
      "end": 14.001,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and also of my brethren.",
      "verse": "10:1",
      "lineIndex": 5
    },
    {
      "start": 14.681,
      "end": 21.368,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "For behold, it came to pass after my father had made an end of speaking the words of his dream,",
      "verse": "10:2",
      "lineIndex": 6
    },
    {
      "start": 21.548,
      "end": 24.613,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and also of exhorting them to all diligence,",
      "verse": "10:2",
      "lineIndex": 7
    },
    {
      "start": 24.793,
      "end": 27.115,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "he spake unto them concerning the Jews\u2014",
      "verse": "10:2",
      "lineIndex": 8
    },
    {
      "start": 27.795,
      "end": 29.931,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "That after they should be destroyed,",
      "verse": "10:3",
      "lineIndex": 9
    },
    {
      "start": 30.111,
      "end": 32.294,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "even that great city Jerusalem,",
      "verse": "10:3",
      "lineIndex": 10
    },
    {
      "start": 32.474,
      "end": 35.678,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and many be carried away captive into Babylon,",
      "verse": "10:3",
      "lineIndex": 11
    },
    {
      "start": 35.858,
      "end": 38.505,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "according to the own due time of the Lord,",
      "verse": "10:3",
      "lineIndex": 12
    },
    {
      "start": 38.685,
      "end": 40.264,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "they should return again,",
      "verse": "10:3",
      "lineIndex": 13
    },
    {
      "start": 40.444,
      "end": 43.184,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "yea, even be brought back out of captivity;",
      "verse": "10:3",
      "lineIndex": 14
    },
    {
      "start": 43.364,
      "end": 46.429,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and after they should be brought back out of captivity",
      "verse": "10:3",
      "lineIndex": 15
    },
    {
      "start": 46.609,
      "end": 49.953,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "they should possess again the land of their inheritance.",
      "verse": "10:3",
      "lineIndex": 16
    },
    {
      "start": 50.633,
      "end": 52.537,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Yea, even six hundred years",
      "verse": "10:4",
      "lineIndex": 18
    },
    {
      "start": 52.717,
      "end": 55.55,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "from the time that my father left Jerusalem,",
      "verse": "10:4",
      "lineIndex": 19
    },
    {
      "start": 55.73,
      "end": 58.888,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "a prophet would the Lord God raise up among the Jews\u2014",
      "verse": "10:4",
      "lineIndex": 20
    },
    {
      "start": 59.068,
      "end": 60.368,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "even a Messiah,",
      "verse": "10:4",
      "lineIndex": 21
    },
    {
      "start": 60.548,
      "end": 62.081,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "or, in other words,",
      "verse": "10:4",
      "lineIndex": 22
    },
    {
      "start": 62.261,
      "end": 63.933,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "a Savior of the world.",
      "verse": "10:4",
      "lineIndex": 23
    },
    {
      "start": 64.613,
      "end": 67.074,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And he also spake concerning the prophets,",
      "verse": "10:5",
      "lineIndex": 24
    },
    {
      "start": 67.254,
      "end": 70.133,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "how great a number had testified of these things,",
      "verse": "10:5",
      "lineIndex": 25
    },
    {
      "start": 70.313,
      "end": 72.031,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "concerning this Messiah,",
      "verse": "10:5",
      "lineIndex": 26
    },
    {
      "start": 72.211,
      "end": 73.883,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "of whom he had spoken,",
      "verse": "10:5",
      "lineIndex": 27
    },
    {
      "start": 74.063,
      "end": 75.967,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "or this Redeemer of the world.",
      "verse": "10:5",
      "lineIndex": 28
    },
    {
      "start": 76.647,
      "end": 80.502,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Wherefore, all mankind were in a lost and in a fallen state,",
      "verse": "10:6",
      "lineIndex": 29
    },
    {
      "start": 80.682,
      "end": 82.215,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and ever would be",
      "verse": "10:6",
      "lineIndex": 30
    },
    {
      "start": 82.395,
      "end": 84.624,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "save they should rely on this Redeemer.",
      "verse": "10:6",
      "lineIndex": 31
    },
    {
      "start": 85.304,
      "end": 87.951,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And he spake also concerning a prophet",
      "verse": "10:7",
      "lineIndex": 32
    },
    {
      "start": 88.131,
      "end": 90.407,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "who should come before the Messiah,",
      "verse": "10:7",
      "lineIndex": 33
    },
    {
      "start": 90.587,
      "end": 92.491,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "to prepare the way of the Lord\u2014",
      "verse": "10:7",
      "lineIndex": 34
    },
    {
      "start": 93.171,
      "end": 96.515,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Yea, even he should go forth and cry in the wilderness:",
      "verse": "10:8",
      "lineIndex": 35
    },
    {
      "start": 96.695,
      "end": 98.692,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Prepare ye the way of the Lord,",
      "verse": "10:8",
      "lineIndex": 36
    },
    {
      "start": 98.872,
      "end": 100.73,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and make his paths straight;",
      "verse": "10:8",
      "lineIndex": 37
    },
    {
      "start": 100.91,
      "end": 104.068,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for there standeth one among you whom ye know not;",
      "verse": "10:8",
      "lineIndex": 38
    },
    {
      "start": 104.248,
      "end": 106.059,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and he is mightier than I,",
      "verse": "10:8",
      "lineIndex": 39
    },
    {
      "start": 106.239,
      "end": 109.722,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "whose shoe's latchet I am not worthy to unloose.",
      "verse": "10:8",
      "lineIndex": 40
    },
    {
      "start": 109.902,
      "end": 112.967,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And much spake my father concerning this thing.",
      "verse": "10:8",
      "lineIndex": 41
    },
    {
      "start": 113.647,
      "end": 117.78,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And my father said he should baptize in Bethabara, beyond Jordan;",
      "verse": "10:9",
      "lineIndex": 42
    },
    {
      "start": 117.96,
      "end": 120.654,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and he also said he should baptize with water;",
      "verse": "10:9",
      "lineIndex": 43
    },
    {
      "start": 120.834,
      "end": 123.806,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "even that he should baptize the Messiah with water.",
      "verse": "10:9",
      "lineIndex": 44
    },
    {
      "start": 124.486,
      "end": 127.226,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And after he had baptized the Messiah with water,",
      "verse": "10:10",
      "lineIndex": 45
    },
    {
      "start": 127.406,
      "end": 129.496,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "he should behold and bear record",
      "verse": "10:10",
      "lineIndex": 46
    },
    {
      "start": 129.676,
      "end": 132.184,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that he had baptized the Lamb of God,",
      "verse": "10:10",
      "lineIndex": 47
    },
    {
      "start": 132.364,
      "end": 135.011,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "who should take away the sins of the world.",
      "verse": "10:10",
      "lineIndex": 48
    },
    {
      "start": 135.691,
      "end": 139.313,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass after my father had spoken these words",
      "verse": "10:11",
      "lineIndex": 50
    },
    {
      "start": 139.493,
      "end": 142.883,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "he spake unto my brethren concerning the gospel",
      "verse": "10:11",
      "lineIndex": 51
    },
    {
      "start": 143.063,
      "end": 145.524,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which should be preached among the Jews,",
      "verse": "10:11",
      "lineIndex": 52
    },
    {
      "start": 145.704,
      "end": 148.955,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and also concerning the dwindling of the Jews in unbelief.",
      "verse": "10:11",
      "lineIndex": 53
    },
    {
      "start": 149.135,
      "end": 151.271,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And after they had slain the Messiah,",
      "verse": "10:11",
      "lineIndex": 54
    },
    {
      "start": 151.451,
      "end": 152.566,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "who should come,",
      "verse": "10:11",
      "lineIndex": 55
    },
    {
      "start": 152.746,
      "end": 154.604,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and after he had been slain",
      "verse": "10:11",
      "lineIndex": 56
    },
    {
      "start": 154.784,
      "end": 156.502,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "he should rise from the dead,",
      "verse": "10:11",
      "lineIndex": 57
    },
    {
      "start": 156.682,
      "end": 158.958,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and should make himself manifest,",
      "verse": "10:11",
      "lineIndex": 58
    },
    {
      "start": 159.138,
      "end": 160.531,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "by the Holy Ghost,",
      "verse": "10:11",
      "lineIndex": 59
    },
    {
      "start": 160.711,
      "end": 162.104,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "unto the Gentiles.",
      "verse": "10:11",
      "lineIndex": 60
    },
    {
      "start": 162.784,
      "end": 166.035,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Yea, even my father spake much concerning the Gentiles,",
      "verse": "10:12",
      "lineIndex": 61
    },
    {
      "start": 166.215,
      "end": 168.955,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and also concerning the house of Israel,",
      "verse": "10:12",
      "lineIndex": 62
    },
    {
      "start": 169.135,
      "end": 172.432,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that they should be compared like unto an olive tree,",
      "verse": "10:12",
      "lineIndex": 63
    },
    {
      "start": 172.612,
      "end": 175.259,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "whose branches should be broken off",
      "verse": "10:12",
      "lineIndex": 64
    },
    {
      "start": 175.439,
      "end": 178.922,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and should be scattered upon all the face of the earth.",
      "verse": "10:12",
      "lineIndex": 65
    },
    {
      "start": 179.602,
      "end": 181.831,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Wherefore, he said it must needs be",
      "verse": "10:13",
      "lineIndex": 66
    },
    {
      "start": 182.011,
      "end": 186.469,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that we should be led with one accord into the land of promise,",
      "verse": "10:13",
      "lineIndex": 67
    },
    {
      "start": 186.649,
      "end": 189.668,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "unto the fulfilling of the word of the Lord,",
      "verse": "10:13",
      "lineIndex": 68
    },
    {
      "start": 189.848,
      "end": 193.656,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that we should be scattered upon all the face of the earth.",
      "verse": "10:13",
      "lineIndex": 69
    },
    {
      "start": 194.336,
      "end": 197.169,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And after the house of Israel should be scattered",
      "verse": "10:14",
      "lineIndex": 70
    },
    {
      "start": 197.349,
      "end": 199.764,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "they should be gathered together again;",
      "verse": "10:14",
      "lineIndex": 71
    },
    {
      "start": 199.944,
      "end": 201.384,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "or, in fine,",
      "verse": "10:14",
      "lineIndex": 72
    },
    {
      "start": 201.564,
      "end": 205.326,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "after the Gentiles had received the fulness of the Gospel,",
      "verse": "10:14",
      "lineIndex": 73
    },
    {
      "start": 205.506,
      "end": 208.014,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "the natural branches of the olive tree,",
      "verse": "10:14",
      "lineIndex": 74
    },
    {
      "start": 208.194,
      "end": 210.516,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "or the remnants of the house of Israel,",
      "verse": "10:14",
      "lineIndex": 75
    },
    {
      "start": 210.696,
      "end": 212.368,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "should be grafted in,",
      "verse": "10:14",
      "lineIndex": 76
    },
    {
      "start": 212.548,
      "end": 215.381,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "or come to the knowledge of the true Messiah,",
      "verse": "10:14",
      "lineIndex": 77
    },
    {
      "start": 215.561,
      "end": 217.651,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "their Lord and their Redeemer.",
      "verse": "10:14",
      "lineIndex": 78
    },
    {
      "start": 218.331,
      "end": 220.607,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And after this manner of language",
      "verse": "10:15",
      "lineIndex": 79
    },
    {
      "start": 220.787,
      "end": 224.316,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "did my father prophesy and speak unto my brethren",
      "verse": "10:15",
      "lineIndex": 80
    },
    {
      "start": 224.496,
      "end": 226.307,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and also many more things",
      "verse": "10:15",
      "lineIndex": 81
    },
    {
      "start": 226.487,
      "end": 228.763,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which I do not write in this book;",
      "verse": "10:15",
      "lineIndex": 82
    },
    {
      "start": 228.943,
      "end": 234.191,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for I have written as many of them as were expedient for me in mine other book.",
      "verse": "10:15",
      "lineIndex": 83
    },
    {
      "start": 234.871,
      "end": 237.75,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And all these things, of which I have spoken,",
      "verse": "10:16",
      "lineIndex": 84
    },
    {
      "start": 237.93,
      "end": 240.391,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "were done as my father dwelt in a tent,",
      "verse": "10:16",
      "lineIndex": 85
    },
    {
      "start": 240.571,
      "end": 242.243,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "in the valley of Lemuel.",
      "verse": "10:16",
      "lineIndex": 86
    },
    {
      "start": 242.923,
      "end": 245.338,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass after I, Nephi,",
      "verse": "10:17",
      "lineIndex": 88
    },
    {
      "start": 245.518,
      "end": 247.933,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "having heard all the words of my father,",
      "verse": "10:17",
      "lineIndex": 89
    },
    {
      "start": 248.113,
      "end": 251.364,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "concerning the things which he saw in a vision,",
      "verse": "10:17",
      "lineIndex": 90
    },
    {
      "start": 251.544,
      "end": 255.724,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and also the things which he spake by the power of the Holy Ghost,",
      "verse": "10:17",
      "lineIndex": 91
    },
    {
      "start": 255.904,
      "end": 259.108,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which power he received by faith on the Son of God\u2014",
      "verse": "10:17",
      "lineIndex": 92
    },
    {
      "start": 259.288,
      "end": 262.307,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the Son of God was the Messiah who should come\u2014",
      "verse": "10:17",
      "lineIndex": 93
    },
    {
      "start": 262.487,
      "end": 264.995,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I, Nephi, was desirous also",
      "verse": "10:17",
      "lineIndex": 94
    },
    {
      "start": 265.175,
      "end": 268.704,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that I might see, and hear, and know of these things,",
      "verse": "10:17",
      "lineIndex": 95
    },
    {
      "start": 268.884,
      "end": 270.695,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "by the power of the Holy Ghost,",
      "verse": "10:17",
      "lineIndex": 96
    },
    {
      "start": 270.875,
      "end": 272.733,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which is the gift of God",
      "verse": "10:17",
      "lineIndex": 97
    },
    {
      "start": 272.913,
      "end": 275.467,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "unto all those who diligently seek him,",
      "verse": "10:17",
      "lineIndex": 98
    },
    {
      "start": 275.647,
      "end": 277.133,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "as well in times of old",
      "verse": "10:17",
      "lineIndex": 99
    },
    {
      "start": 277.313,
      "end": 281.818,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "as in the time that he should manifest himself unto the children of men.",
      "verse": "10:17",
      "lineIndex": 100
    },
    {
      "start": 282.498,
      "end": 285.888,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "For he is the same yesterday, today, and forever;",
      "verse": "10:18",
      "lineIndex": 101
    },
    {
      "start": 286.068,
      "end": 288.576,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the way is prepared for all men",
      "verse": "10:18",
      "lineIndex": 102
    },
    {
      "start": 288.756,
      "end": 290.939,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "from the foundation of the world,",
      "verse": "10:18",
      "lineIndex": 103
    },
    {
      "start": 291.119,
      "end": 294.091,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "if it so be that they repent and come unto him.",
      "verse": "10:18",
      "lineIndex": 104
    },
    {
      "start": 294.771,
      "end": 297.79,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "For he that diligently seeketh shall find;",
      "verse": "10:19",
      "lineIndex": 105
    },
    {
      "start": 297.97,
      "end": 301.314,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the mysteries of God shall be unfolded unto them,",
      "verse": "10:19",
      "lineIndex": 106
    },
    {
      "start": 301.494,
      "end": 303.305,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "by the power of the Holy Ghost,",
      "verse": "10:19",
      "lineIndex": 107
    },
    {
      "start": 303.485,
      "end": 306.225,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "as well in these times as in times of old,",
      "verse": "10:19",
      "lineIndex": 108
    },
    {
      "start": 306.405,
      "end": 309.424,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and as well in times of old as in times to come;",
      "verse": "10:19",
      "lineIndex": 109
    },
    {
      "start": 309.604,
      "end": 312.715,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "wherefore, the course of the Lord is one eternal round.",
      "verse": "10:19",
      "lineIndex": 110
    },
    {
      "start": 313.395,
      "end": 316.367,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Therefore remember, O man, for all thy doings",
      "verse": "10:20",
      "lineIndex": 111
    },
    {
